title: Vegetarian Stall at Koufu Woodlands Mart
description: Chinese-style vegetarian stall in a neighborhood food court with vegan options. Opens before 8am. Serves a wide variety of food, including a vegetables such as okra, long bean, bittergourd, curry veg which are served with vermicelli, noodles and more. A la carte dishes like udon, hor fun and mee goreng are available later in the day.
